==English==
=== Noun ===
#An [[actor]] who is a [[woman]] or a [[girl]].

===Usage notes===
*[[Word|Words]] like ''actress'', ''[[aviatrix]]'', and ''[[doctress]]'' stem from attempts to impose Latin grammar on the English language.  Since in English the [[suffix]] -''or'' does not convey [[masculinity]] a [[feminine]] [[counterpart]] is [[unnecessary]].  ''Actress'' should be avoided unless it is necessary to [[indicate]] the actor is [[female]].

